                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1903-18511027 t18511027-1903-punishment-70"></join>Confined Three Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Cresswell.</hi>
